        "TileImage": "$($repository 3e1bb865-3209-46b8-b345-d5b8e0428084).Image",
        "Description": "Agent 47, your next mission requires you to don the guise of a Sniper Ninja, a heroic and charming master of stealth, as part of our contract with a local kids&apos; television show. You will need to use your signature sniper rifle to eliminate the dastardly villians hidden among the Hokkaido staff and patients.  If done quick, we can wrap up filming before lunchtime! Good luck, 47.",
